Huayi Compressor (Jingzhou) Co., Ltd. one of the four compressor factories of Huayi group, is located in Jingzhou city, Hubei province, China. It is a leading professional manufacturer of R134a, R600a and R290 hermetic compressors for small refrigerators, freezers, water dispensers, water coolers, wine coolers, icemakers, showcases and other refrigerating devices, as well as automobile DC compressors. It is ranked top in compressor industry in China, with an annual production output of over 5 million compressors and USD180 million turnover.
Equipped with high-caliber R&D team and state-of-the-art production lines, we are able to exploit and develop new compressors and refrigeration production. We offer an array of voltage refrigeration compressors including 110V, 127V, 220V, 250V and DC compressors. Featuring with lower noise, slight vibration, lower starting voltage, higher efficiency, less energy consumption and longer lifetime, our Huayi compressors have passed the testing and identification of the Institute of Chinese Home Appliances, meanwhile, achieved national CCC authentication, ISO9001-2000, UL, VDE, CUL, CB, INMETRO and other international certificates,.. see more info

